user_query: I am planning a road trip with my friends and we want to listen to our favorite songs. Can you provide us with the download URLs for the MP3 versions of the songs 'Dance Monkey' and 'Blinding Lights'? We would also like to know the direct download links and titles of the latest music videos of 'Billie Eilish' and 'Justin Bieber'.

TaskList.description: Find and retrieve the download URLs for the MP3 versions of the songs 'Dance Monkey' and 'Blinding Lights'.
Find and retrieve the latest music videos for 'Billie Eilish' and 'Justin Bieber', including their direct download links and titles.
